            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>honey</strong> and <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> in a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>– this is your<strong> honey-mustard glaze</strong></p><p>Wrap each <strong>sausage</strong> in 1 and 1/2 strips of <strong>bacon </strong>– these are your<strong> pigs in blankets</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1666964974762-x200.jpg",
