            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pigs in blankets </strong>to a separate<strong> baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Pour over the<strong> honey-mustard glaze</strong> and reserve the bowl</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until cooked through – these are your <strong>honey mustard pigs in blankets</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1666964983001-x200.jpg",
