      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fries are golden and crisp, remove the tray from the oven and add the <strong>stuffing crumble</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and return the tray for a final 4-5 min<strong> </strong>– these are your<strong> stuffing fries</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
