    {
      "instruction": "<p>Layer your <strong>toasted brioche base </strong>with some of the <strong>apple salad</strong> and<strong> </strong>2 <strong>honey mustard pigs in blankets</strong></p><p>Dollop over some of the <strong>truffle mayo </strong>and top with a <strong>toasted brioche lid</strong> – this is your <strong>honey mustard pigs in blankets brioche</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>honey mustard pigs in blankets brioche </strong>with the <strong>stuffing fries</strong>, <strong>remaining apple salad </strong>and <strong>truffle mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
